original_solution:
Solve the equation $3x = 12 - 5x$:

\[
\begin{align*}
3x + 5x &= 12 \\
8x &= 12 \\
x &= \frac{12}{8} \\
x &= \frac{3}{2}
\end{align*}
\]

\[
\boxed{\frac{3}{2}}
\]

